---
import "../../../styles/home/home.css";
---

<div class="service-row section">
  <div class="service-text">
    <span class="service-tag">For Speed & Security</span>
    <h3>High-Performance Static Sites</h3>
    <p>
      Imagine a website that loads instantly, never gets hacked, and needs zero
      maintenance. I build these using Astro. Since there is no database, these
      sites are incredibly secure and fast.
    </p>
    <div class="best-for-box">
      <strong>Best for:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Personal Portfolios & Resumes</li>
        <li>Landing Pages for Ads</li>
        <li>Documentation Sites</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="service-image">
    <img
      src="/assets/Icons/create-wordpress-business-website.png"
      alt="Static Site"
    />
  </div>
</div>
